      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/19/157749474/26b9736a2d14fc4162b2448963f45695_1634566290879285492.png",
                "id": "talent19875",
                "key": "熠辉轨度剑",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "熠辉轨度剑"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素战技</span></p><p>生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">安眠帷幕护盾</span>和<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">飞星</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">安眠帷幕护盾</span></strong></p><p>提供2点护盾，保护我方出战角色。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">飞星</span></strong></p><p>我方角色使用技能技能，累积1枚「晚星」。如果「晚星」已有至少4枚，则消耗4枚「晚星」，造成1点冰元素伤害。（生成此出战状态的技能，也会触发此效果）</p><p>重复生成此出战状态时：累积2枚「晚星」。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/19/157749474/de48c78ad3dc782b2dfe98bbe645f7cd_5585331550167684761.png",
                "id": "talent78318",
                "key": "垂裳端凝之夜",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "垂裳端凝之夜"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成3点<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素伤害</span>，召唤<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">饰梦天球</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/19/157749474/1af1d6edbe77aedd11a2e57551afb598_806465183359666090.png",
                "id": "talent71899",
                "key": "星流摇床之梦",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "星流摇床之梦"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">结束阶段：</span>造成1点冰元素伤害。如果飞星在场，则使其累积1枚「晚星」。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/19/157749474/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_1385263495223683725.png",
                "id": "talent53942",
                "key": "饰梦天球",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/19/157749474/8fae1317e614df75bd7911789c244c1f_6246954186092095649.png",
                "title": "饰梦天球"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着冰元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超导</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">冻结</span>：本伤害+1，使目标本回合无法行动（受到物理或火元素伤害后提前解除，但是伤害+2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/19/157749474/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_4018101681212500730.png",
                "id": "talent28551",
                "key": "冰元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/19/157749474/1ef525b101a31611b9fe2cc1b0a59aa8_3890628921788465176.png",
